As a chaebol, shouldn't you be polite to your customers?

20
00:01:21,410 --> 00:01:23,350
This bitch is funny.

21
00:01:23,350 --> 00:01:28,840
I knew you weren't one of us the first time I saw you.

22
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:31,710
So you were a customer, huh?

23
00:01:31,710 --> 00:01:33,110
Okay.

24
00:01:33,110 --> 00:01:35,730
I will treat you like a queen.

25
00:01:36,270 --> 00:01:37,920
In bed.

26
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:39,700
Let go. I said let go!

27
00:01:39,700 --> 00:01:41,420
I liked your rebellious spirit.

28
00:01:41,420 --> 00:01:42,950
I know people like you well.

29
00:01:42,950 --> 00:01:45,410
Stop being coy. Come here.

30
00:01:47,250 --> 00:01:48,740
What's going on?

31
