Why not? It has all the major food groups.

80
00:04:54,950 --> 00:04:56,220
Didn't you like what I ordered?

81
00:04:56,220 --> 00:04:58,270
Are you asking after I've ordered what I want?

82
00:04:58,270 --> 00:04:59,840
You're the one following me.

83
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:02,060
Don't eat it if you don't want to.

84
00:05:02,060 --> 00:05:03,530
I have to eat it because you ordered it.

85
00:05:03,530 --> 00:05:06,280
Since we're among the people, there are no chocolate drinks.

86
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:09,010
You only drink espresso.

87
00:05:11,090 --> 00:05:13,360
I'm very thirsty.

88
00:05:15,020 --> 00:05:16,650
What will you do next?

89
00:05:16,650 --> 00:05:18,870
It's too late now. How will you keep track of me?

90
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:20,060
Are you going to stay awake?

91
00:05:20,060 --> 00:05:21,850
Or will you sleep with me?

92
00:05:21,850 --> 00:05:23,660
