93
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:26,290
Even if I wanted to, I couldn't reveal his private life.

94
00:05:26,290 --> 00:05:28,440
If you sue me, I won't be able to pay you.

95
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:30,460
I have nothing but debt.

96
00:05:30,460 --> 00:05:35,350
Why would I want to be fired from the highest-paying company?

97
00:05:35,350 --> 00:05:37,650
Hooray!

98
00:05:39,020 --> 00:05:41,350
It's so cute. Do you like it?

99
00:05:41,350 --> 00:05:42,600
What a shame.

100
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,950
