104
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:56,990
Sweet? That thing?

105
00:05:56,990 --> 00:05:59,570
Yes. Right?

106
00:05:59,570 --> 00:06:01,620
Go home.

107
00:06:01,620 --> 00:06:05,670
- Excuse me? - I said, finish this and go home.

108
00:06:05,770 --> 00:06:07,430
You can't get it back.

109
00:06:07,430 --> 00:06:09,590
I'll have this packaged.

110
00:06:10,940 --> 00:06:13,350
Baek Su Jeong's danger level has been lowered.

111
00:06:13,350 --> 00:06:17,050
He has better taste than I thought.

112
00:06:29,630 --> 00:06:31,750
How much is this already?

113
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:35,540
I can sell it for at least three million.

114
00:06:36,670 --> 00:06:39,410
I still have to return it.

115
00:06:44,770 --> 00:06:46,960
Why isn't this working? Oh no.

116
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:49,150
