117
00:06:49,150 --> 00:06:52,490
It's not mine and it's not coming out.

118
00:06:53,310 --> 00:06:54,920
It worked!

119
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:58,160
Oh my God, seriously.

120
00:06:58,160 --> 00:07:00,810
