126
00:07:15,510 --> 00:07:17,110
At work.

127
00:07:17,110 --> 00:07:19,420
Wow, you can take over now.

128
00:07:19,420 --> 00:07:21,450
That's why I learned it, in the first place.

129
00:07:21,450 --> 00:07:23,250
I also obtained an electrician's license.

130
00:07:23,250 --> 00:07:26,340
You know I work on this every day after work, right?

131
00:07:26,340 --> 00:07:30,200
