135
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,610
I like it when it's quiet.

136
00:07:44,610 --> 00:07:47,570
I promoted it on Instagram, but it didn't work.

137
00:07:47,570 --> 00:07:50,340
But it worked.

138
00:07:50,340 --> 00:07:51,660
