148
00:08:16,540 --> 00:08:19,580
The food needs to look delicious.

149
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:28,360
Doesn't this look more impressive?

150
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,340
Get a loan...

151
00:08:30,340 --> 00:08:32,090
Composition is important in photographs.

152
00:08:32,090 --> 00:08:37,400
You either emphasize the entire opening or you do a close-up.

153
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,880
Really?

154
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:47,700
You can't show anything else alongside it.

155
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:49,700
Like this.

156
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:55,530
- Like this? - Do something like this.

157
00:09:12,100 --> 00:09:14,200
