168
00:10:44,370 --> 00:10:46,610
To go fishing.

169
00:10:50,050 --> 00:10:51,460
Thank you.

170
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:53,370
You didn't have to bring me here.

171
00:10:53,370 --> 00:10:55,910
I have some time before I go to work. Can I watch you?

172
00:10:55,910 --> 00:10:57,170
