179
00:11:14,210 --> 00:11:16,390
I think I should stop.

180
00:11:16,390 --> 00:11:18,890
I need to go to work.

181
00:11:18,890 --> 00:11:20,180
Go on then.

182
00:11:20,180 --> 00:11:23,020
I had fun last night thanks to you.

183
00:11:23,020 --> 00:11:24,810
See you later.

184
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:32,510
Anne!

185
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:33,880
