186
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:36,600
Huh? I'm not late. I arrived right on time.

187
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:38,050
That's too late.

188
00:11:38,050 --> 00:11:39,844
Buying the goods at their original prices...

189
00:11:39,856 --> 00:11:42,200
...if you want, you need to come early and help us.

190
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:44,430
Have you ever seen a thief with a conscience?

191
