Seriously. Don't be so proud.

192
00:11:46,010 --> 00:11:48,170
Okay, how's your shop?

193
00:11:48,170 --> 00:11:50,700
Ha Jeong says she doesn't have any customers.

194
00:11:50,700 --> 00:11:52,150
