202
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:18,590
I dated a guy for 10 years and then I married him. Have you forgotten?

203
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:22,710
Dad, what are the good deals today?

204
00:12:22,710 --> 00:12:23,810
Coral.

205
00:12:23,810 --> 00:12:26,750
