219
00:12:59,250 --> 00:13:02,090
It could be your voice.

220
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:04,470
Okay, I'll do it.

221
00:13:04,470 --> 00:13:06,850
You need to pay him back.

222
00:13:12,730 --> 00:13:15,460
What was that little head shake?

223
00:13:32,610 --> 00:13:36,570
I told you. This isn't my style.

224
00:13:37,250 --> 00:13:39,310
